{"tid":2490392,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一轉天氣加埋戴口罩搞到爛面","createTime":"2021-04-15T14:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T14:23:05.000Z","uid":25953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a9bcb605dd509736c2add577c8d7229b21b46187","tid":2490392,"uid":25953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"話說上年4月開始我兩邊面開始起粒粒又紅色一撻撻<br />\n去睇醫生醫生話係戴口罩係社會嘅錯<br />\n食咗3個月抗生素係咁搽藥膏都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我都唔記得佢7月個陣咩事自己好返啲<br />\n而嚟到今年...<br />\n我又開始爛面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又痕又核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔想出街食飯 一除口罩實嚇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問有冇巴絲都有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想嚟圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0852e53e1ae2fdfd234c7edb29a210d6c57cb92","tid":2490392,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"人生太短出手要更大"}]}